headline: MAN to supply 1,200 semitrailer tractors to Gartner KG by 2028
summary: The agreement allows for the delivery of up to 350 vehicles per year, featuring the new MAN PowerLion drivetrain.

headline: Gartner’s Alex Bant breaks down the new realities of CFO leadership
summary: Bant explains how CFOs can make better decisions, challenge the single source of truth, lead under PE, reduce workflow drag and prepare teams for an AI-driven future.
